Papa cambiar la pagina por defectode epache o xampp

Change DocumentRoot and Directory path in /opt/lampp/etc/httpd.conf from

DocumentRoot "/opt/lampp/htdocs" and Directory "/opt/lampp/htdocs"

 restart apache and go to the localhost see in actionx-> /opt/l mpp/lampp starts
 url ->l http://127.0.07.1 localhost 
